PanelRedirect - ChangeLog
=========================

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Version 1.1.1
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

	Fixed: Solving Apache 503 "Service temporarily unavailable" error

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Version 1.1.0
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

	Added: required_api info field
