	Fixed: Override HTTP ports which are defined by i-MSCP in case of proxy usage

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Version 1.0.5
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

	Added: Checks for update tasks

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Version 1.0.4
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

